      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REMISSION RUN (1) gave a start after a chequered run when hampered to finish a 14 length eighth (18.49) at this track in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance. SHE'S SILKY (6) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a third place finish (18.09) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. One of the main contenders. SUDDENLY I SEE (2) has a strong record this trip with two wins and two placings from six starts. Below best last time at The Gardens (23.16) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length fourth. Makes strong appeal on best. RACCOON RHIA (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
